---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Writing
description: Notes and writing by Harikrishna Sahu.
section: writing
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
  <h1>Research notes, paper thoughts, and practical materials informatics essays.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Short essays on polymer informatics, machine-learning workflows, research software, and lessons from recent papers.</p>
</section>

<section class="post-index">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="post-row">
      <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
      <div>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          {% if post.data.sample %}<span class="sample-badge">sample draft</span>{% endif %}
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            {% if tag != "posts" %}<span>{{ tag }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
